soot.util.annotations

Class AnnotationInstanceCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.util.annotations.AnnotationInstanceCreator

  • public class AnnotationInstanceCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple helper class with the ability to create an instance of Proxy implementing the annotation interface represented by the given AnnotationTag.

    • Method Detail

      • create

        public java.lang.Object create(AnnotationTag tag)
        Creates an instance of the Annotation represented by tag.
        Parameters:
        tag - the soot internal representation of the annotation to be created.
        Returns:
        an Object extending Proxy and implementing the type of tag
        Throws:
        java.lang.RuntimeException - if
        • the class defined in AnnotationTag.getType() of tag could not be loaded.
        • tag does not define all required methods of the annotation loaded.
        • a class defined within a AnnotationElem could not be loaded.
        • the enum defined in AnnotationEnumElem is no instance of Enum.
